  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK865">
<l>vaḻinōkkāṉ vāyppaṉa ceyyāṉ paḻinōkkāṉ </l>
<l>paṇpilaṉ paṟṟārk kiṉitu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>(A) pleasing (object) to his foes is he who reads not moral works, does nothing that is enjoined by them cares not for reproach and is not possessed of good qualities.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
